    technical skill an bora of judo high cathegories: Abstract. - Moscow, 1985. - 24 p.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">4. Jmarev N., Leonenko I. Run 800 м. Target system
    model of perennial training / Light athletics,1979, № 6. - p. - 18 - 20.</font></p>
    <p style="text-indent: 40; text-align: justify"><font size="2">5. Timakova Т.S. Perennial preparing a swimmer and its
